Class GraphvizPreferencePage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.jface.dialogs.DialogPage
      • org.eclipse.jface.preference.PreferencePage
        • org.eclipse.jface.preference.FieldEditorPreferencePage
          • org.eclipse.gef.dot.internal.ui.GraphvizPreferencePage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, IDialogPage, IMessageProvider, IPreferencePage, IPropertyChangeListener, IWorkbenchPreferencePage

    public class GraphvizPreferencePage
extends FieldEditorPreferencePage
implements IWorkbenchPreferencePage
    Store and access the path to the 'dot' executable in the preference store. The path can be set by the user, using a file selection dialog. The selected location is stored in the bundle's preferences and available from there after the initial setting.
